snippet.title: Skopje - Gameplay Overview Тrailer
snippet.description:
This is a first gameplay overview with alpha footage of Skopje, explaining the story, combat, roguelite and other elements of the game.


Wishlist Skopje on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1211980/Skopje/

Explore a city thrust into disarray by an unknown event and survive the hordes of mutated abominations that lurk at every corner.
https://skopjegame.com/

Join Discord: https://discord.gg/THJ4d3t
